{"type": "article", "id": 29903, "title": "旅行包", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-20T23:04:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160720220503aT0GELz2sCRYJDZw.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>为旅行打包行李经常会让人头疼不已，<a href=\"http://www.keeppursuing.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">KP</a> 公司最近推出了一款同时注重分隔功能与时尚外型的旅行包，它流畅的线条或许会让人联想到公路上驰骋的跑车。旅行包内置了针对各种装备的口袋：令人头疼的鞋子可以收纳进透气排湿的大口袋里；正前方和侧面的隔间则用来放置需要经常取用的小物；正上方还为平板电脑设计了一个内衬袋，不仅方便拿取，也减少了机器和其他行李的碰撞。旅行包还拥有独特的防盗功能，将拉链穿过一旁的织物小环后如果有人拉动拉链，用户就会感受到拉力。每款旅行包还附赠一个洗浴袋和六个与其配套的分装瓶，这些瓶子都按照美国运输安全局的登机规定打造，用户可以轻松通过安检。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.keeppursuing.com/shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 188 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720221005emZi8lB56Ldj9NO0.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607202210057fvp6KjWuqi0CVks.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.426000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720221005aW36OMwqxlkD7jyH.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720221006mFIq5nve3sft9WHT.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.896000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}